Name: Get-KSTelephoneNumber
Description: Get a telephoneNumber and otherTelephone based on the IPPhone value.

Name: Import-KSADTelephoneNumber
Description: Import ipPhone, othertelephone and telephoneNumber from an Excel spreadsheet supplied by BT.

Name: Update-KSDDIMapping
Description: Update the ddi-mapping.xml file from a spreadsheet.
